<i>♪ When I was just a little boy ♪</i>

126
00:08:13,370 --> 00:08:15,747
<i>♪ I asked my father ♪</i>

127
00:08:15,747 --> 00:08:17,749
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

128
