<i>♪ Of my own ♪</i>

138
00:09:03,878 --> 00:09:06,381
{\an8}<i>♪ They ask their father ♪</i>

139
00:09:06,381 --> 00:09:08,633
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

140
00:09:08,633 --> 00:09:09,926
♪

141
00:09:09,926 --> 00:09:12,554
<i>♪ "Will I be pretty?" ♪</i>

142
